### Register user
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ishaan",
  "password": "securepass123"
}

###  Login
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ishaan",
  "password": "securepass123"
}

### Store a secret (paste your token from login response below)
